data.description: This cherished neighborhood gem has been meticulously maintained and regularly updated by its long-term owner. With a touch of reluctance due to retirement and a shift towards downsizing, this beloved home is now on the market. All appliances convey, furniture is negotiable. Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the historic Jefferson neighborhood! This stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem is a timeless blend of historic charm and modern elegance. Step inside to discover a gourmet kitchen featuring sleek granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, perfect for creating culinary masterpieces. As you explore further, you'll be captivated by the spacious master bedroom, flooded with natural light pouring in through several windows. Pamper yourself in the luxurious master bath, complete with a double vanity and a refreshing stand shower. Plus, enjoy the convenience of a secondary master bedroom with its own private bath, ideal for guests or family members. Escape to your own private sanctuary in the enclosed patio, where you can relax and unwind in peace. Step outside to discover the ultimate backyard oasis, complete with an inground pool and hot tub, creating the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings and summertime fun. And with solar panels in place, you can enjoy energy-efficient living while reducing your carbon footprint. Situated on a spacious corner lot, this home offers both privacy and curb appeal. Not to mention, new Energy efficient windows, recent pool plaster, and brand new fence in front yard! Don't miss your chance to own a piece of history in one of San Antonio's most coveted neighborhoods. Schedule your showing today and experience the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and style!
